            "state": "translated",
            "value": "未连接任何设备"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Only USB 2.0 is active. If you expected high speed, the cable may not support it.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "仅 USB 2.0 活跃。如果您期望高速，线缆可能不支持。"
